  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic implant wear credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA-based wear prediction of a total knee replacement tibial insert under physiological loading conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case polyethylene wear operating conditions for a Class II orthopedic implant at Model Risk Level 3. Full 13-factor assessment covering all ASME V&V 40-2018 credibility factors at rigor appropriate for MRL 3.",
