    "intendedUse": "Use FEA to identify worst-case operating conditions for polyethylene wear across 6 alignment-load combinations for a Class II total knee replacement tibial insert. Results compared against physical wear simulator data using relative wear volume (RW < 1.15 acceptance criterion relative to predicate device).",
